================================================================================
1. What is This Project
================================================================================

This project is an end-to-end replay and research toolkit for the ChatGPT Team
subscription protocol. It reverses the protocol chain from mitmproxy packet captures
and implements it as a runnable client, for:

  - Protocol analysis and replay in CTF (Capture The Flag) challenges
  - Security research within explicitly in-scope assets of public bug bounty programs
    (HackerOne / Bugcrowd / etc.)
  - Adversarial ML research on visual CAPTCHA systems such as hCaptcha
  - Research and education in browser automation anti-detection techniques

Empirical research materials regarding anti-fraud mechanisms in the toolkit are
published as public security knowledge, in the same tradition as CAPTCHA breaking,
fingerprinting attacks, and adversarial ML in academic literature.

