9. Regarding the hCaptcha Solver
================================================================================

The visual solver in CTF-pay/hcaptcha_auto_solver.py is an independently usable
research product. We publish it because:

  - Whether visual CAPTCHAs can be automatically solved is already an open academic
    question
  - hCaptcha's design assumption is that "solvers require human annotation + model
    training"; this project demonstrates the "VLM zero-shot decision" approach that
    emerged between 2024–2026
  - No CAPTCHA system's security should be built on "the adversary hasn't seen the
    internal details"

If you work at hCaptcha / Intuition Machines and have concerns about the solver's
use in your production environment, please contact us through Security Advisory. We
have no interest in publishing research that would make genuinely effective abuse
prevention systems harder to operate.

